; CHECK-NEXT:    [[TMP0:%.*]] = bitcast i32* [[SCALAR_GEP]] to <4 x i32>*
; CHECK-NEXT:    [[WIDE_LOAD:%.*]] = load <4 x i32>, <4 x i32>* [[TMP0]], align 4
